Package: blockr.lm
Title: Linear Model Blocks for blockr
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    c(person(given = "Christoph",
             family = "Sax",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "christoph@cynkra.com",
             comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7192-7044")))
Description: Extends 'blockr.core' with interactive blocks for statistical model
    fitting and diagnostics. Users can build and explore linear and generalized
    linear models through a graphical interface, including coefficient tables,
    ANOVA tables, diagnostic plots, and interactive residual exploration.
URL: https://github.com/blockr-org/blockr.lm
